{%- comment -%}
  Custom Liquid template for Shopify policy pages (/policies/refund-policy,
  /policies/privacy-policy, /policies/terms-of-service, /policies/shipping-policy).

  Policy pages do NOT support JSON templates, so sections are wired up here in
  Liquid instead of a .json template:
    - breadcrumbs  : Start / <policy title>
    - main-policy  : the policy content (page_title + page_description)

  The "image grid above the footer" (store-grid-group section group) can't be
  rendered from a template — {% raw %}{% sections %}{% endraw %} is layout-only — so it is injected for
  policy pages in layout/theme.liquid instead.
{%- endcomment -%}
{% section 'breadcrumbs' %}
{% section 'main-policy' %}
